metadata.description: Dead Handz is a collection of 666 unique NFTs cast out of The Portal and onto the Ethereum blockchain. The Portal was created by 5 mysterious individuals, known as The Activators, who have their own cryptic backstories and each bring a special utility to the tokens. Dead Handz NFT owners have access to the Dead Handz universe, which includes The Laboratory, Khonsuâ€™s Telescope and The Portal. This is the first exclusive and interactive story told through the world of NFTs. This is only the beginning... Visit www.deadhandz.com for more details.
